  "text": "The results confirm the importance of house prices for household borrowing. There is quite strong evidence suggesting that house prices are positively correlated with household debt overhang. This is consistent with the findings by Fernandez-Corugedo and Muellbauer (2006), [CITATION_1] , as well as by Aoki and others (2004) .",
